QuestData.Title: Feed the Eater
QuestData.Description:
The House of Plagues has suffered calamity, much like Lordaeron. I hope that our work and effort here will reverse some of that destruction.
But first, we must reach farther into the House of Plagues so we can strengthen the capabilities of Faranell's plague eater.
Any slime or creature you slay will surely help it gain fortitude.
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay Slimes and Plaguerocs in the House of Plagues.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Meet Calia Menethil deeper in the House of Plagues.
